Job Responsibility:

1. Collaborate with product managers to develop high-quality audio and video related new features aligned with business needs;

2. Participate in the development of Android Audio and Video SDK in the multimedia platform, including short video shooting, recording, image editing, and other related fields;

3. Responsible for research on new technologies in the Audio and Video fields and implementation in Audio and Video SDK.

Job Requirements:
- Experiences in platforms: Web, Android, and IOS
